# This repo intentionally tracks only the silver price alert project.
# Other files in this working directory (customer data, DB configs, etc.)
# are local-only and must never be committed.
*
!silver_price_alert/
!silver_price_alert/**
!.gitignore
!.github/
!.github/**

# Local-only files within the tracked project
silver_price_alert/.venv/
silver_price_alert/**/__pycache__/
silver_price_alert/**/*.pyc
